info.title: EPOS WebAPI
info.description:
This is the newest version of the EPOS set of APIs, based on a based on a subdivision of services.
This suite allows you to search for data and metadata, and then to download or process search results.
GUI http://nodedev.bgs.ac.uk/epos/epos-gui/master/ gui (webapi client)
SWAGGER http://epos.cineca.it/webapi/swagger-ui.html swagger gui (webapi client development)
Generated for Spring Framework EPOS ICT-C server input via RabbitMQ Enjoy!

Contacts:

EPOS Web Api Team apis@lists.epos-ip.org
